Codehaus support 
 
  Codehaus offers the following systems to support open source development. 
 
*--------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
|| Application                                                 || URL                               ||  Description                                                                            ||
*--------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| {{{http://openxource.com/xircles/}Xircles}}                  | {{http://xircles.codehaus.org}}    | Maintain your personal settings (except Jira credentials, which is not part of the LDAP) |
*--------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| {{{http://www.atlassian.com/software/jira}Jira}}             | {{http://jira.codehaus.org/}}      | Issue tracker                                                                            |
*--------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| {{{http://www.atlassian.com/software/bamboo}Bamboo}}         | {{http://bamboo.ci.codehaus.org/}} | Continuous Integration Server                                                            |
*--------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| {{{http://www.atlassian.com/software/fisheye}Fisheye}}       | {{http://fisheye.codehaus.org/}}   | Source Repository Viewer                                                                 |
*--------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| {{{http://www.atlassian.com/software/confluence}Confluence}} | {{http://docs.codehaus.org/}}      | Wiki                                                                                     |
*--------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| {{{http://www.sonarsource.org}Sonar}}                        | {{http://sonar.ci.codehaus.org/}}  | Code Quality Management System                                                           |
*--------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| IRC                                                          | {{http://irc.codehaus.org/}}       | IRC Webclient for Codehaus Internet Relay Chat                                           |
*--------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
 
  There's a personal webspace available for every committer. Due to {{{http://jira.codehaus.org/browse/HAUS-2187}HAUS-2187}} it's not generated automaticly, instead you have to ask for it.